{
  "texts": [
    "The agents may also call external functions or databases to enhance their assessments or predictions.Step 4: Synthesis of Findings.",
    "After each agent completes its task, the results are sent back to the Planning Agent.",
    "This agent synthesizes the findings from all the specialists, creating a comprehensive response that integrates all aspects of the problem, from drug efficacy and safety to enrollment potential.Step 5: Reasoning and Final Decision Making.",
    "The final step involves applying the ReAct reasoning method to the synthesized findings.",
    "Here, the Planning Agent, enhanced by few-shot learning capabilities, examines the context and details of the integrated response to make informed decisions."
  ]
}